                title="A legacy of trust and innovation"
                subtitle="Lucky Group of Companies is a diversified business group operating across specialized subsidiaries, combining sector experience with disciplined execution."
              />

              <AboutList>
                <AboutPoint>
                  <span className="dot" />
                  <div>
                    <h4>Construction</h4>
                    <p>Residential and commercial building solutions focused on long-term value.</p>
